com.betfair.cougar.core.api.ev

Interface ExecutableWrapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Executable

    public interface ExecutableWrapper
extends Executable
    Interface to be implemented by any Executables which wrap other executables. Used by various Cougar internals to find the wrapping they need to implement certain hooks.
